Cape Town - A crash involving a container truck and at least one passenger vehicle has forced the closure of the N1 FW de Klerk Boulevard at Blackriver Parkway near Salt River, Cape Town on Wednesday morning. 

It appears the truck overturned, with its massive shipping container falling off its trailer onto a passenger vehicle. 




